These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, cola, water, sprite, almond-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
3. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking 7up##7
4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |  7   |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk | cola | 7up | milk | tea | water |

