.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, journalist, writer, mechanic, bartender, doctor, fisherman
 1. the writer is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
 2. the writer is somewhere between the fisherman and the journalist##7
 3. the journalist is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 4. the dancer is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
 5. the mechanic is somewhere between the dancer and the bartender##7
 6. the writer is on the left of the bartender##1
 7. the doctor is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 8. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
 9. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
10. the journalist is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3     |    4    |      5      |     6      |   7    |
| Job   | fisherman | writer | bartender | journalist | doctor | mechanic | dancer |

