.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bluemaster, vegafina, dannemann, blend, bolivar, havana
1. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere between the oliveros-smoker and the blend-smoker##7
2. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##7
3. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
4. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere between the havana-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##7
5. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
6. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere between the bluemaster-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
7. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
8. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1  |   2   |   3    |   4   |     5      |  6  |     7      |
| Cigar   | havana | bolivar | vegafina | blend | bluemaster | oliveros | dannemann |

