2. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
5. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsdaisy##2
6. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
7. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsrose##7
8. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
9. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |    7    |
| Flower   | bellflower | rose | tulip | daisy | orchid | azalea | amaryllis |

