.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-5::.
7 different games are played: poker, chess, domino, bridge, go, snooker, backgammon
 1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 2. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 6. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing chess##7
10. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |   3   |  4  |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Game   | snooker | domino | backgammon | poker | chess | go | bridge |

