2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking lemonade##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |      3      |      4       |     5     |    6    |   7   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk | coffee | water | 7up | tea | soy-milk |

