.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-7::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, bike, train, subway, skateboard, jet-ski, motorbike
1. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person driving the jet-ski##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the train##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Transport   | subway | bike | motorbike | train | jet-ski | boat | skateboard |

