 2. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##7
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the cain-smoker##7
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 7. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
10. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1        |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5        |      6      |     7     |
| Cigar   | siglo | cain | pall-mall | ritmeester | oliveros | tiparillo | alhambra |

